latestIgtvVideos.title: Dontia Dental Care
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Since more than  past two years , Dontia Dental Care @dontia.dental.care has been my go to place for any concern regarding my teeth . Recently , I went for my teeth whitening treatment , and it has been such a comfortable and a very quick procedure using the latest technology.The results are amazing and at the same time all safety measures and precautions were being taken for the present situation .
 Sitting at the Dentist's chair at Dontia is comfortable , painless and not scary at all . The entire staff is very friendly and Dr Prabhjeet Singh Sethi @prabs_unltd and Dr Harleen Sahni Sethi @dontia.drharleen has always been my favourite , and have been very welcoming and supportive .. I always have a great experience whenever I visit Dontia and yes of course I smile more confidently and even wider and brighter after my sessions at @dontia.dental.care . 
Thank you so much Dontia Dental Care .
😃😃😃😃😃😃😃

latestIgtvVideos.title: EK KADAM VIKAS KI ORE
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
A year ago , I took a little step towards an initiative to make people realise that a simple step like Washing your hands with Soap and water can save your life ..
I was very fortunate to start this journey with these little kids from @vidhya.ngo with the support of @sushmitaajha and Navaneeta Saha @bong__bhukkad .. 
A year later this turned out to be one of the most important steps to fight the Global Pandemic .
Today on the occasion of Global Hand washing Day , I pledge to continue raising awareness about Hand Hygiene and Clean Hands for all .

Video by @lensstarphotography team
@dietitian.neel.soham

latestPosts.caption:
2024 has been such a good year! Only one word can sum it up... Grateful!! For all the opportunities, for all the dreams re-lived, for dreams coming true, for all the places I have been to, for meeting incredible people along the journey and for celebrating life with loved ones... ❤❤❤
Grateful for all the lessons I have learned but the most important one is to be Content with all that I have and all that I will receive... ✨✨✨ Magic happens when you let go , be in the moment and trust the Universe.. ✨ 
"Oh give thanks to the Lord, for he is good; for his steadfast love endures forever!" Thank you 2024 for an incredible year ✨✨✨
